# Prerequisites on the zTrial Windows system

Users need to ensure the following prereqs are installed:

## Scenario 2: Onboard the Spring Boot REST API in the Zowe API Mediation Layer

- Gradle or Maven build systems
- Be able to edit YAML files

## Scenario 3: Create a desktop app

- Web Browser (typically Firefox in zTrial, for accessing the Zowe Desktop)
- Git (or can be optional if the GitHub code is fetched beforehand on the Windows system)
- JDK (for bulding apps)
- ant, ant-contrib (for building apps)
- NPM

## Scenario 4: Add a new plug-in to Zowe CLI

- Git (or can be optional if the GitHub code is fetched beforehand on the Windows system)
- npm
